thread.title: Jeb Bush raises $13.4 million, more than Rubio and Cruz
thread.title_full: Jeb Bush raises $13.4 million, more than Rubio and Cruz - POLITICO

author: Glenn Thrush
title: Jeb Bush raises $13.4 million, more than Rubio and Cruz
text:
Jeb Bush raised $13.4 million in the third quarter, outpacing both Marco Rubio and Ted Cruz but falling far short of Ben Carson's reportedly $20 million haul. Bush, according to preliminary data provided by the campaign, has $10.3 million in cash on hand.
The full financial disclosure report will be released later Thursday.
